# No-commit-manuscripts policy.
# Manuscripts and supplementary materials are working-tree-only:
# they are needed on disk for PowerShell readiness gates and
# downstream Jupyter / audit workflows, but must not enter Git
# history. See feedback_no_commit_manuscripts_policy.md in
# operations memory for the full rule.
inputs/*.docx
inputs/*.pdf
